Create 3 files for the CitedBy.ai project at C:\Users\User\Documents\citedby-v3. This is a dark-themed (bg-black, text-gray-100) React+Tailwind app with purple accents (#7c3aed). Use lucide-react icons, recharts for charts.

## File 1: types/integrations.ts (~50 lines)

```typescript
export type IntegrationType = 'ga4' | 'search-console';

export interface Integration {
  id: string;
  type: IntegrationType;
  name: string;
  email: string;
  property: string; // GA4 property or SC site
  connectedAt: string;
  status: 'connected' | 'disconnected' | 'error';
}

export interface AttributionKPI {
  aiVisits: number;
  aiConversions: number;
  aiTrafficShare: number; // percentage
  aiAvgCTR: number; // percentage
}

export interface TrafficDataPoint {
  date: string;
  chatgpt: number;
  perplexity: number;
  claude: number;
  gemini: number;
  copilot: number;
}

export interface AttributionRow {
  source: string;
  visits: number;
  pageViews: number;
  avgDuration: string; // "2m 34s"
  bounceRate: number;
  conversions: number;
  trend: number; // percentage
}

export interface AIQuery {
  query: string;
  clicks: number;
  impressions: number;
  ctr: number;
  position: number;
  isAIReferral: boolean;
}
```

## File 2: services/integrations.ts (~180 lines)

localStorage key: `citedby_integrations`.

Functions:
- `getIntegrations(): Integration[]`
- `connectIntegration(type: IntegrationType): Promise<Integration>` - Simulate 2s OAuth flow, create mock integration with realistic Google email/property
- `disconnectIntegration(id: string): void`
- `getAttributionKPIs(period: '7d' | '30d' | '90d'): AttributionKPI` - Return mock data scaled by period
- `getTrafficData(period: '7d' | '30d' | '90d'): TrafficDataPoint[]` - Generate daily data points (7/30/90 entries). Each AI source: chatgpt 30-150, perplexity 10-60, claude 15-80, gemini 20-90, copilot 5-40
- `getAttributionTable(): AttributionRow[]` - 5 rows: ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, Gemini, Copilot with realistic data
- `getAIQueries(): AIQuery[]` - 10 mock queries with isAIReferral = true for ~60%

## File 3: pages/Integrations.tsx (~450 lines)

Full Integrations page.

Props: `{ onBack: () => void; user: User | null; onDeductCredits: (amount: number) => boolean; }`

Import User from '../types'.

### Structure:
- Header: "Intégrations" gradient-text + badge "3 Gas / sync"
- 2 connection cards side by side (GA4 + Search Console):
  - If not connected: icon, name, description, "Connecter" button (triggers simulated OAuth with loading spinner)
  - If connected: green status, email, property name, "Déconnecter" button
- Attribution dashboard (visible if >= 1 integration connected):
  - Period selector: 7j | 30j | 90j
  - 4 KPI cards: Visites IA (number), Conversions IA (number), Part trafic IA (%), CTR moyen IA (%)
  - AreaChart (recharts): Traffic by AI source over time with gradient fills (ChatGPT=emerald, Perplexity=blue, Claude=purple, Gemini=amber, Copilot=cyan)
  - Attribution table: source, visits, pages vues, durée, taux de rebond, conversions, tendance (+/- with color)
  - Top requêtes IA section: list of queries with badge "IA" for isAIReferral

Use AreaChart with stacked areas. Style with ninja-card class, bg-[#111111] for inputs.

IMPORTANT: Write ONLY these 3 files. Do not modify any other files.

